### IsNegated {#a78a0916b4e753daa2448c0d34c61d226}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>bool anonymous&#95;namespace&#123;BasicAliasAnalysis.cpp&#125;::VariableGEPIndex::IsNegated</>}>
True if the index should be subtracted rather than added.

We don&#39;t simply negate the Scale, to avoid losing the NSW flag: X - INT&#95;MIN&#42;1 may be non-wrapping, while X + INT&#95;MIN&#42;(-1) wraps.
